TITLE: Accessing Row Selection State in TypeScript
DESCRIPTION: Demonstrates how to access various row selection states using TanStack Table APIs. This includes getting the raw selection state, selected rows, filtered selected rows, and grouped selected rows.
SOURCE: https://github.com/TanStack/table/blob/main/docs/guide/row-selection.md#2025-04-19_snippet_0

LANGUAGE: typescript
CODE:
```
