TITLE: Implementing Fully Controlled Table State in Angular
DESCRIPTION: Demonstrates how to completely control table state in Angular by using the onStateChange option. This approach hoists the entire table state into your own state management system and shows initialization techniques.
SOURCE: https://github.com/TanStack/table/blob/main/docs/framework/angular/guide/table-state.md#2025-04-19_snippet_3

