TITLE: Incorrect Data Mutation Pattern
DESCRIPTION: Demonstrates an anti-pattern where data mutations destroy stable references and cause infinite rendering loops.
SOURCE: https://github.com/TanStack/table/blob/main/docs/faq.md#2025-04-19_snippet_2

LANGUAGE: javascript
CODE:
```
export default function MyComponent() {
  const columns = useMemo(() => [
    // ...
  ], []);

  const { data, isLoading } = useQuery({
    //...
  });

