TITLE: Creating an Angular Table with createAngularTable
DESCRIPTION: Demonstrates how to use the createAngularTable function to create a table instance in an Angular component. It uses signals for reactive data management.
SOURCE: https://github.com/TanStack/table/blob/main/docs/framework/angular/angular-table.md#2025-04-19_snippet_0

LANGUAGE: typescript
CODE:
```
import {createAngularTable} from '@tanstack/angular-table'

export class AppComponent {
  data = signal<Person[]>([])

  table = createAngularTable(() => ({
    data: this.data(),
    columns: defaultColumns,
    getCoreRowModel: getCoreRowModel(),
  }))
}
```

